	<section class="about-section">
		<h2>Getting Started</h2>
		<ol>
			<li>Install the NuGet package: <code>PanoramicData.Blazor.WebGpu</code></li>
			<li>Register services in <code>Program.cs</code>:
				<pre><code>builder.Services.AddPDWebGpu();</code></pre>
			</li>
			<li>Add a WebGPU container to your Razor page:
				<pre><code>&lt;PDWebGpuContainer FrameRateMode="FrameRateMode.Fixed" TargetFrameRate="60"&gt;
    &lt;!-- Your WebGPU content here --&gt;
&lt;/PDWebGpuContainer&gt;</code></pre>
			</li>
		</ol>
